== Degmadda Wanlaweyne (Daafeet) == 
----------------------------------------------
Degmada '''Wanlweyne''' (Daafeet) waa degmo ka tirsan degmooyinka Shabeellaha Hoose waxaa hostaga tuulooyin farabadan oo garaya ila '''400''' tuulo. Dhaqaalaha dadka degmada ay ku tirsan yihin waxaa ka mida beeraha, iyo xoolaha nool. Degmadan waxaa ku yaala garoonka caalamiga ee BALIDOOGLE Airport. Odayaasha ayaa maamula degmada. 

Degmada w/wayne, beesha '''Hubeer''' wa beesha kaliya ee ugu badan degmadaasi marki lo eego beelaha walaalahoda ee la degan. Degmada wanlaweyn wa xarunta ugu weyn ee beesha Hubeer degto marki lo eego gobolada Baay, Gedo, iyo Jubooyinka, maxa yeelay degmada w/weyn waxa wada degan afarta lafod ee ka koban tahay beesha Hubeer wexeyna degmadasi ku leyihin golle odayal dhaqaameed oo qadimi ah awoodne leh lona yaqano (Hubeer Hirine) oo marki af maxaga lo fasiro la micno ah Hubeerka mideysaan ama isku xirran.

Gollaha odayasha ee Hubeer hirinaha wuxu ka koban yahay afarta lafod ee beesha Hubeer wexeyna isku wada racsan yihin in malaaqa beesha Hubeer u yahay malaaq Adan Xusein malaaq, lakin inkastoo malaq Adan uu howlgab yahay kunna sugan yahay magalada muqdisho waxa howsha u uu wakiishay duq sarkaalka ahna nabadoonka guud ee beesha Hubeer Nabadoon Xusein Axmed Caliyow oo ku suggan degmada daafeet.

Gollaha odayasha ee Hubeer hirinaha daafeet waxa ay fasax siiyeen in gobolada alto-jubba ay doran karan malaaq ayaga u gooni ah madama beeshu ay aad u ballaran tahay, goboladasne ay aad uga fogyihin gobolka sh/hoose oo ah xarunta malaaqa guud ee beesha Hubeer. Hadaba, xilka Malaqnimo ee gobolada alto-jubba ee beesha Hubeer waxa hada hayaa malaaq Xasan Shurre Maxamuud ahna gudoomiyaha odayasha dhaqanka DigilMirifle.

Beesha Hubeer, dhaqan ahan malaaq wuxu kaga dhigan yahay abaandulle, oo mar walba u tagan difaaca shacabka, iyo deganada beesha. Hadaba, malaaqa guud ee beesha Hubeer waxa dhaqan ahan lagu caleemo sara guriga yarranka beesha ee Huliye ee Reereeji gar ahan Lafta Cumaroow qaasatan jufada reer Adde oo aad lo qadarriyo wanne lafta u malaaqa guud u ka amar qato wixi talo iyo tusaale ah maddama jufa Adde ee yihin dadka maalgeeliya beesha Hubeer daafeet hadi lacale beelo kale ay is qabtan.

Hadaba, malaaqa guud hadu lacale u duqobo ama howlgab noqdo, waxa uun codsan kara in la bedelo jufada hose ee reer Adde. Haddi lacale lafaha qarkoda ee beesha Hubeer ka koban tahay ay isku qabsadan "Dooro biyoo macabto iyo way cabta" waxa la racaa talada jufada reer Adde oo ah halka ugu dambeyso ee garta lagu qoyo. Dhaqankani ee beesha Hubeer ay ledahay wa dhaqan soojireen ah oo ay ku dhaqmi jireen kumanan sano kahor.

Degmada w/weyn waxa lagu qiyaasay '''1 Milyaan qoys''' oo Hubeer wada ah hadi lagu darro dadka degan tulooyinka fog-fog ee xududaaha laaleh degmooyinka dariska ah.    

